You've got the SharePoint basics covered. You've even dabbled in some of the more advanced functionality. Now you are looking for more. This biweekly series explores some of SharePoint's hidden gems: the need-to-knows, the gotchas, and plenty of cool "I had no idea this existed" functionality.
